channel.title: 317 Project/Hosting Help/Hey!
channel.description:
Hey guys, It's been awhile. How is everyone? Anyways, I realize this is in the wrong Topic so please do not leave a comment saying so, because I realize. XD :D I love you guys and you are a inspiration for my coding <3 I am working on a new project and found a nice base to work on. I can no longer find it on MoparScape under Server Downloads so I'm hoping one of you guys have the link! It's a 317 and it has Bh, Fremmy Island, etc. Any luck? Please comment.
Anyways, I am willing to help these new guys with there servers and I will setup your computers so you can host your own very servers! If you would like help leave a comment below or add my msn. (MrCommunityGaming@live.com)
Thanks guys! Please comment!
